<br>
My simple answer for all loot distribution problems is this: &quot;It depends on the situation&quot;.<br>
<br>
Obviously there isn't one system which will work for every guild.  And, every guild probably doesn't use the same exact system for every situation, from a mega-raid to a 1-group XP session.<br>
<br>
I'm associated with 2 guilds on two servers.  One does tier 5 and 6 mobs and has a loot committee.  It's a small guild, but manages to take on bigger mobs with less people, better discipline and greater knowledge.  The LC system works very well for this guild.<br>
<br>
My other guild is comprised mainly of RL friends and will probably never get past a tier 1 or tier 2 mob (this is the guild my warrior's in).  In this guild, its almost as difficult to get someone to take something as it is to get something to drop in the first place.  Everyone else always says &quot;No, you take it.&quot;.  Luckily we're small enough that we have very few class conflicts.  If there was a conflict...two people wanting something...then a simple roll will suffice.<br>
<br>
If the system in your guild isn't working for you, and just you, then you might consider leaving.  But, if the loot system isn't working for your guild as a whole, research, begin dialogue and help to create a system or systems which are more beneficial for your members.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showMessageRange?topicID=5351.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showMessageRange?topicID=5351.topic&start=41&stop=42>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showPrevMessage?topicID=5351.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showNextMessage?topicID=5351.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.emailToFriend?topicID=5351.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.threadControl?topicID=5351.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5351.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5351.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 borde